Package xxl.core.spatial.converters

Provides tools for converting Point and Key Pointer Elements that are stored in ASCII-format to a binary representation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsciiKPEConverter
    An AsciiKPEConverter can be used to convert KPE-Objects that are stored in ASCII-format to a binary representation.
    AsciiPointConverter
    An AsciiPointConverter can be used to convert Point-Objects that are stored in ASCII-format to a binary representation.

Package xxl.core.spatial.converters Description
